title: Week 6 Recap 2022
description:
Field Yates, Daniel Dopp and Liz Loza recap everything you need to know from Week 6 of the NFL season including a few breakout players who could be lineup locks going forward. Plus, Liz and Daniel give an audio exclusive reaction to SNF including how important Dak’s return is to the Cowboys’ fantasy weapons.
